---
title: Ginger Beef Rice Bowl with Pickled Onion & Japanese Mayo
description: Add tons of flavour to your beef with a tasty sauce mixture plus loads of veggies, then fill your bowl with a bed of rice, pickled onion, fresh cucumber and a sensational mayo. This is a recipe for a bowl you won't forget!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ginger-beef-rice-bowl-2321ceb1.jpg
